18:16.527 --> 18:19.095
I was having a party and
I called our weed guy

18:19.129 --> 18:20.763
and I said give me
a pound of both.

18:20.797 --> 18:23.398
I don't know how you order coke
'cause I don't really do it.

18:23.432 --> 18:26.767
- You're not that dumb.
- Are you kidding?

18:29.437 --> 18:31.137
No, wait... we can
sell that, bro.

18:31.171 --> 18:34.306
You know you forgot about my
son's little league game, right?

18:34.340 --> 18:35.874
Oh fuck.

18:35.908 --> 18:38.909
- I was up really late.
- Yeah, you kinda went crazy on me.

18:38.944 --> 18:40.878
<i>- Crazy?
- What, you don't remember?</i>

18:40.913 --> 18:43.648
