out, but you were being a pussy.

18:43.682 --> 18:47.184
- I wouldn't exactly call that crazy.
- You kicked my truck.

18:47.218 --> 18:48.451
I did not.

18:48.486 --> 18:51.254
Vince, you know I came
out here for myself,

18:51.288 --> 18:53.623
but now I see there was maybe
a bigger purpose for my visit.

18:53.657 --> 18:58.026
The ex-addict who I
invited into my home

18:58.061 --> 19:00.829
<i>has come down from God
to save me?</i>

19:00.863 --> 19:03.931
From what?
Oh, let's see.

19:03.965 --> 19:05.766
I forgot to go to
your son's baseball game?

19:05.800 --> 19:08.602
I mean, why a movie
star has to show up

19:08.636 --> 19:11.703
to an eight-year-old's
baseball game is beyond me.

19:11.738 --> 19:14.039
But hey, I guess
that's Hollywood, right?

19:14.073 --> 19:17.708
Did I wake you up last night?
I'm so sorry.

19:17.743 --> 19:20.811
- And what did I ever do to you, Turtle?
- Nothing, Vin.

19:20.845 --> 19:23.980
- Or you, Johnny?
- Nothing.

19:24.014 --> 19:27.649
So why the fuck are you all here?
Oh wait, let me guess.

19:27.683 --> 19:30.217
E orchestrated it.

19:30.252 --> 19:33.587
E's worried about me.
E's always worried that his golden goose

19:33.621 --> 19:36.256
<i>- - is going to implode.
- Take it easy, Vince.</i>

19:36.290 --> 19:39.759
- It was my idea.
- That's really disappointing, Johnny.

19:39.793 --> 19:42.995
Because I'm fine.
I just had an argument with my girl

19:43.029 --> 19:45.030
and I'm a little upset, okay?
That's all!

19:45.064 --> 19:47.866
- I know, I talked to her.
- Really? And what did she say?

19:47.900 --> 19:49.501
She said you went crazy
on her too, Vince.

19:49.535 --> 19:51.636
- She doesn't want to speak
to you anymore. - Good!

19:51.671 --> 19:53.438
Because I don't really want
to speak to her either.

19:53.473 --> 19:55.574
- - Or any of you.
- Vine... Vince, come on.

19:55.608 --> 19:57.442
No, I'm serious.
I'm gonna go for a walk.

19:57.477 --> 20:01.043
And I know you all need me, but
I'll call you if I need any of you.

20:04.580 --> 20:06.747
Ahem, well,
Pete berg's office called

20:06.782 --> 20:09.283
and he needs to be at the studio
tomorrow for a camera test.

20:09.317 --> 20:11.885
So which one of you losers is going
to make sure that he gets there?

20:11.919 --> 20:13.820
You're the most powerful
agent in town, Ari.

20:13.854 --> 20:16.222
Why don't you make sure
he gets there?

20:22.294 --> 20:24.728
<i>- - How is she doing?
- She's a little better.</i>

20:24.763 --> 20:26.964
But she's... drunk.

20:26.998 --> 20:29.900
- Drunk? - Yeah, and she
wants to go to Vegas.

20:29.934 --> 20:32.035
Tomorrow she can go to Vegas.
Tonight I need her here.

20:32.070 --> 20:35.538
Marci, get off the phone.
You look like my douche of a husband.

20:35.573 --> 20:38.374
Okay.
I'm doing the best I can.

20:38.408 --> 20:40.909
Do better and I will put
your kids through college too.

20:40.944 --> 20:43.211
Bye, Ari.

20:45.748 --> 20:48.216
Johnny, I'm fine.
I got a room at the Roosevelt.

20:48.250 --> 20:50.585
Bro, I'm sorry.
It was all out of love.

20:50.619 --> 20:52.987
- Please come back.
- I just want to be alone right now.

20:53.021 --> 20:55.489
<i>- - I don't think you should be.</i>

20:55.523 --> 20:57.391
I'll call you if I need you.

20:58.760 --> 21:00.694
Hold on.

21:03.498 --> 21:04.931
<i>Room service.</i>

21:04.966 --> 21:07.667
Coming.

21:10.405 --> 21:11.938
<i>- - Hey, Mr. chase.</i>

21:11.973 --> 21:13.907
Hey.

21:13.941 --> 21:15.942
