with the music?

21:15.976 --> 21:18.044
Sorry about that, Mr. chase.
There's a party.

21:18.079 --> 21:20.080
- Oh yeah? Any good?
- It's Eminem's.

21:20.114 --> 21:22.982
- Can't imagine it isn't.
- Well, I'll probably head up there.

21:23.017 --> 21:25.085
- All right.
- See ya.

21:36.397 --> 21:38.798
I'm sorry I couldn't say
more and let's obviously

21:38.832 --> 21:40.566
keep the Vince stuff
on the d.L.

21:40.601 --> 21:43.202
Turtle, look, if Vince is going
to be the face of Avion,

21:43.237 --> 21:45.804
then obviously we don't want
to hurt his name either.

21:45.839 --> 21:49.007
