23:54.213 --> 23:56.581
Aside from the fact
that she's blessed

23:56.615 --> 23:58.716
by my credible gene pool,

23:58.750 --> 24:01.254
she's also blessed

24:01.288 --> 24:03.256
with an awful lot of my money.

24:03.291 --> 24:06.326
