25:25.593 --> 25:27.427
Can I talk to you in private?

25:32.466 --> 25:35.067
Ari, it's 9:15.
You asked me to do an hour.

25:35.102 --> 25:36.802
Please play longer.
I can't pay your fee,

25:36.837 --> 25:38.237
but I'll give you
the deed to my house.

25:38.271 --> 25:40.705
